Visual prompt 2.1
create a watercolor portrait of a mother and son on paper, use a brush to create small strokes that resemble beach waves in the background. Use bright colors on their  attire to contrast with the sand and beach water. leave white spots untouched to allow them to be the brightest spots and appear at wave foam. Allow fine lines to show joyful facial expressions on the portrait protaganist
